{"tid":1365542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[膠到盡] [P仔] 我正式宣布，將7月27日定為香港人節","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T17:27:00.000Z","uid":287952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"49993865c3b7217e33cca758a51ff0102bfde6f3","tid":1365542,"uid":287952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:16:03.000Z","msg":"元朗多野食多野玩就係香港人都知，平時又唔會入，第一屆就先係元朗搞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經有巴打整理左個日可以有咩活動安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1364901/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1364901/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n咁到時你中意/以為有 D咩HOCC見面會呀，乜撚讀經班呀，就自己埋堆囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂，咁你話開開心心黎過節，先知道偉大既李同志仲有咁多人記得，感動得濟撐下場都無損當日holiday mood既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁又可以搞下fashion show, 近排最流行既頭盔口罩 襯返件大會T，加把遮，都係一種制服誘惑黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔岩去了解下香港法定古蹟，直頭係一路行街一路學香港歷史<br />\n再老土D，重溫下通街跑捉精靈既7事，可能仲會比你捉到隻神獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然，過節唔知起源唔緊要，最重要知過緊咩節，識分幾時食月餅幾時食糉。同樣，唔拎返幾張紀念海報先走，就真係等於無去過呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想講既係，既然大家要對抗白色恐怖，就要搵個正面既目標去取代恐懼。食玩買香港人最叻架啦，呢個時候難到我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbusiness as usual, business everywhere <br />\n<br />\n咁意猶未盡，黎緊個個禮拜六慶祝一下香港人節，都OK喎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想改變大家對727 既觀感。策略照做，散水要快，但態度要變，文宣組請出手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔駛驚失焦，728上環再郁過，陸續有黎"},{"pid":"081ffb9e4362bdea2f474522d1aa6c3b6d94eec1","tid":1365542,"uid":30332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:17:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a189205c84584509f0af58b9eca92d9887f72f4","tid":1365542,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06271e66a57debfe1b95bfcd35e2bfcf1702e3c2","tid":1365542,"uid":278712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:19:14.000Z","msg":"［救港行動］7.26 機場集會某程度上仲緊要過7.27 。外國唔發旅遊警示，會唔會有好客香港人發關愛旅客嘅民間旅遊警示？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364962\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364962</a><br />\n<br />\n聽日！726！機場接機大堂有集會！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363275\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363275</a><br />\n<br />\n↠↠↠ 聽 日 機 場 集 會 !!! ↞↞↞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1362863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1362863</a><br />\n<br />\n7月26日 上午有新鴻基V Walk商場開幕 下午有機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354855</a><br />\n<br />\n[突發] 7月26 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354319</a><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，八仙過海。"},{"pid":"ce108679754783334535fe848e2c81e472326eec","tid":1365542,"uid":287952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:27:00.000Z","msg":"推一次就算"}]}